high_descs: walk to face counter between sinks
pick up candle stick from counter
turn right to face cabinet below sink on right
put candle inside bottom right cabinet
turn around to face toilet
pick up candle stick from toilet tank
walk to face sink cabinets
put candle inside bottom right cabinet
anns.task_desc: put two candles inside bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter on the left by the sink.
Pick up the candle on the counter.
Bring the candle to the right sink.
Put the candle in the right cabinet under the right sink.
Turn around, move to the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the toilet.
Bring the candle to the right sink.
Put the candle away in the right cabinet under the right sink, right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles away in the right cabinet under the right sink.

high_descs: Make a left to walk to the two sinks.
Pick up the candlestick from in between the two sinks.
Turn to face the cabinet below the rightmost sink.
Put the candlestick in the right cabinet below the rightmost sink.
Turn around to walk to the toilet.
Pick up the other candlestick from the lid of the toilet tank.
Walk to face the cabinet below the rightmost sink.
Put the other candlestick in the right cabinet below the rightmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two candlesticks away below the rightmost sink.
